" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 505px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Congenital hernia of the diaphragm",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 485px; height: 627px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The baby in picture A is a normal newborn baby. The baby in picture B has a congenital hernia of the diaphragm. In this condition, the diaphragm (the layer of muscle that separates the organs in the chest from the organs in the belly) has a hole in it. Because of this, organs in the belly move through the hole into the chest.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
